node.title: Woman missing in Taupō area found alive and well
node.description: A woman reported missing in the Kinloch area of Taupō two days ago has been found alive and well this morning.
node.content:
["A woman reported missing in the Kinloch area of Taupō two days ago has been found alive and well this morning.", "", "
Jan-Marie Burton Photo: Supplied / Police
", "Jan-Marie Burton was reported missing by her family after being last seen on Wednesday.", "Police launched an investigation after some of her clothing was found on Kinloch Beach.", "They have thanked the public for their assistance in helping find Burton."]
